## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

VMware Tanzu Observability by Wavefront Nozzle has the following requirements:

+ A read-only administrative access to the Doppler Firehose and Cloud Controller.
+ A Wavefront account and API token.
+ A VMware Tanzu Quota with at least 8G of available memory.

